title: on_exit()
brief: Called when the client exits.
----

<p>If you define the function <tt>on_exit</tt> it will be called when the client is terminated.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre>
function on_exit()
   print("on_exit() called");
end
</pre>
<p class="seealso">See also <a href="on_idle.html">on_idle()</a>.</p>